Installation of the BisonVert client
====================================

Dependencies
------------

BisonVert depends on few existing django apps and packages:
* python-oauth2, from http://github.com/ametaireau/python-oauth2
* django-oauthclient, from http://bitbucket.org/makinacorpus/django-oauthclient
* the excellent restkit lib, by Beno√Æt Chesneau: http://github.com/benoitc/restkit/

Installation
------------

First, you need to get the sources from our github or bitbucket account. there
is also a mirror github powered repository here: , just in case.
    

Once the source fetched, you need to configure it:

OAuth
~~~~~
Create a `settings_local.py` file, and fill it with these options::

    # Session configuration
    SESSION_COOKIE_NAME = 'youcookiename'

    # settings for the local oauth consumer
    OAUTHCLIENT_CONSUMER_KEY = "your.consumer.key.here"
    OAUTHCLIENT_CONSUMER_SECRET = "you.consumer.secret.here"
